column4: Exam not required is the individual's status in completing exams required for graduate or doctoral degree programs.
Exam required but not taken is the individual's status in completing exams required for graduate or doctoral degree programs.
Exam waived is the individual's status in completing exams required for graduate or doctoral degree programs.
Exam taken and passed is the individual's status in completing exams required for graduate or doctoral degree programs.
Exam taken and failed is the individual's status in completing exams required for graduate or doctoral degree programs.
